 - fixed broken handling of SVO/SVD/SVP "bit depth" gadget
 - slightly increased size of SVO/SVD/SVP "bit depth" gadget
 - fixed bug in preferences (controlpad) handling which could
   have lead to crashes and was memory-inefficient anyway;
