V1.40 (1.1.2004):

 - added "BatchProcess" CLI/Shell tool, that allows automatic,
   batched file conversion (optionally with wildcards)
   and upto 4 SVOperators to be applied before conversion,
   e.g. load PNG, antique, toptobottom, anyto24bit, ditherfix24,
   save as JPEG
