        And please think twice before asking - my postbox
        is not unlimited in size.

        * Do not send binaries via Fido or Fido-Gates ! *

           - Usenet
              >>>   info@ar-kleinert.de
                    Andreas_Kleinert@gmx.de

When reporting any bugs, please don't forget to include a detailed
description of the bug and tell me, if it is reproduceable or not.
Please also mention the version number of SView5 you used and describe
your system configuration (Amiga model 500/.../4000T-060, Kickstart/OS,
RAM, HardDisk, special configurations).

